1. home/workstation.nix: Replace wofi with fuzzel in home.packages (line 15)

2. home/hyprland.nix line 97: Replace the wofi cheatsheet command:
   Old: wofi --dmenu --width 1000 --height 600 -p "Keybindings"
   New: fuzzel --dmenu --width 80 --lines 20 --prompt "Keybindings: "

3. home/hyprland.nix line 173: Replace the app launcher binding:
   Old: "\$mainMod, R, App launcher, exec, wofi --show drun"
   New: "\$mainMod, R, App launcher, exec, fuzzel"
   (fuzzel launches in drun mode by default)

